Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小田島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天你去劍道部拍的她們練習賽的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼只有在拍這個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為其他人沒有拍得價值嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是對方的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  你這是在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等身宣傳板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要拿這東西來做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  如果你認識的話也給我介紹介紹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.03,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第14話\N小莉莉的決意和咀嚼的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有說要加入劍道部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次只是去觀摩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加比賽也純粹是為了湊足人數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經下定決心上高中後不參加任何活動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這樣明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小東東  護具定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  我有國中時候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次記得帶來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我在玩從學生那裡沒收的遊戲機…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙好難打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被其他老師看到不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙要打下半身才有效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前玩過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為都是這個模式的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…被其他老師看到不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  輕鬆取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！我才不承認什麼3D
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲還是要2D才是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sprite萬歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那下次要不要比一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？好啊  想用什麼比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Famicom嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前有過注釋了…スーファミ：スーパーファミコン(Super Famicom)的簡稱，\N任天堂於1990年發行的遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  用MD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MD=MEGA DRIVE，SEGA產主機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確點說  用DUO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PCE-DUO：NEC產卡帶光盤一體機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川老師…你是愛好者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的學生來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  老師你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔥粒…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小東東的稱呼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難選擇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個怎麼說來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意接踵而來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過推薦的還是最上面3個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得啊  小莉莉最好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  老師你覺得呢  哪個最好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的大會就4人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東她…的確很可惜  但是我不會讓她參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小莉莉她很喜歡劍道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東同學她自己也樂在其中的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  樂在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  也不能強拉她進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出啥事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有幹勁啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  去社團活動囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天我值日  你們先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  等會見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮崎同學  今天是你值日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  今天我有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託把我那份也做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說的那麼直白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮…宮崎同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  就你一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…其他人都偷懶跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開小差啊…真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦  我們又不同班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次強拉你來練習賽對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引胴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…很開心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就加入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能考上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能參加部團
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒什麼集中力又很笨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多念書不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有沒有參加部團
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績都一樣爛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說  書念得好  部團活動也能得心應手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然再怎麼用功也是白費嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太單純了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說都能騙她上船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣逼她…好愉快啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的成績表  剛入學時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張  是之前考試的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進步了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我加入了劍道部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上高中後成績退步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因為課程越來越難…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯！是因為你沒有繼續練劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道能夠鍛煉精神以及集中力對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你放棄了  所以念書時的集中力也下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的…的確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我男朋友開始算起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道部裡成績優秀的人非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便哪個都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太厲害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入劍道部的話  也能讓他們幫你念書囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！竟然有這麼棒的特權…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是笨蛋還是遲鈍給我說清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋的話念書也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲鈍的話不就更要練劍道來集中精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對  對  對…對的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其拼小命把成績硬提高一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不努力精進拿手的劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後靠推薦上大學不是更好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要當笨蛋的話  也要做個劍道笨蛋呀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（靠推薦上大學）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽見咚的一聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一定要加入劍道部…才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加入！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我加入劍道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了！讓我加入！讓我加入！求你了！…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…看來挺容易使喚的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:11:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我加入劍道部！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎小莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  東同學也要加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以參加5人的比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東聰莉的稱呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小莉莉」不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  終於湊足五個人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  而且是很好的人才哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照那個陣容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IH大賽預選也值得人期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預選結束後  我們再比一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  不過說實話我是不打算輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也是我們輕鬆取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是另一間學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是不會那麼簡單就被打敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  還要再賭點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…指導者來打賭不怎麼好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎盃不是為了這種事情而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  真要進軍全國的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指導者也要認真考慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你問我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想認真地去做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是顧問該說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要短時間內鍛煉她們的話  就進行合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  在各種準備方面就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也變得像個劍道部的樣子了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚嗎？9點以後的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行啊  你不認真做好顧問工作可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了因為考試不能參加的前輩們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全國大賽進軍吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為部長的你不夠強大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉不到部員的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間明明只有我和紀梨乃兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師為了我又鼓起幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球部的棒球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網球部的網球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橄欖球！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教導主任從3樓掉下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要尋找強者之時所遇到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後小都都也入部了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  和小鞘之間發生了點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那也不是什麼難事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常地去和小鞘道歉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要道歉  是她不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘也打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中堅小鞘你上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要贏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！我一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不能加入劍道部的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼為什麼為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實不喜歡劍道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就很喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…父母說上高中後就不能再練
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也這麼決定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後是東的加入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  現在我不好好栽培她們怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發愁的話怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  現在可沒時間閒玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週末就要比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IH大賽預選
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IH大賽預選…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了別嚇著！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次獲勝之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是全國大賽了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是IH大賽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能帶你們打進全國大賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要學校能認可出眾的我所築建的實績的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那怎麼樣都無所謂的蠢事就能一筆勾銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用辭職也沒事了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！你先在個人戰拿下優勝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把進軍全國的資格搶下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  高中劍道還是要比團體賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團體賽能夠進軍全國才是真正展現指導者實力的表現啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！決定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團體賽打向全國！這才是我獨一無二的生存之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡  有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東  沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有備用的  不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你入部真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡人同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母也很擔心我自不參加部團後成績下降的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  答應讓我加入劍道部再試試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川老師也一同勸說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉川老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  很好啊  東
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不過  成績退步的話還是非要退出不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績優秀組！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面就交給你們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會認真教你的啦  莉莉～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這樣就聚齊5人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大賽上一定也能有出色的表現！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奮鬥吧！我的戰士們！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們男生還是一如既往地被忽略了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在個人戰加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要進一步鍛煉你們以及和東的團隊合作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以本週末進行合宿！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校方面已經批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像部團活動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子才有大賽氣氛啊  紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在哪裡進行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:17:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在學校裡連續兩天的練習！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會徹底的鍛煉你們  做好覺悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…合宿不能到山上呀海邊呀瀑布呀寺院啦之類的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那個錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設備很齊全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少和其他學校一起練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒那個門路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就成了平日的練習了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  作為補償  町戶高的女生會一起過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合練習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町戶高是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你前輩的學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  男生也會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生不會來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把男生也叫來就沒裁判了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無視我們了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺越來越正式了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君有合宿過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  中學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來小珠你是頭一回？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然練習很嚴格  但晚上大家鬧得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧得很開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過男生只有兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君又有小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  下個週末
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就麻煩您獨自吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因為是部團活動嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿嗎…在什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生也一起住在學校嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中田家的…那個…勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就是那個勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和那個勇次君一起住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要搞錯內容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,250元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:50.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這也不忘超劍戰隊的錄影嗎小珠！）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合…宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}透きとおる陽射しが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}みんなの背中輝いているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:21.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}同じ日々目指してるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:27.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう寂しくならないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:32.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰もひとりぼっちじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心まで立ち止まる時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その笑顔でみんなが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:41.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}見守ってくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから眩しさに飛びこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}青空に届く{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ひるまずにひたすらに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この道を行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いつかときめきの頂点に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}生まれるよ虹の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}苦しくて焦っても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}乗り越えられるきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私たちの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:13.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.11,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:58.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}{\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}喜歡著純淨的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:15.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我們的背後都閃耀著光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:21.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}每一日都朝著同一個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:27.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就再也不會感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:32.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}誰也不會是孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}若是心中彷徨無法前進的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我會用這份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:41.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}把大家守護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}因此光彩奪目地展翅高飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}那份力量直達藍天之上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}毫不畏懼  毫不分心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}向著前程全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}直到心跳的頂點時分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就會綻放出彩虹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}就算再多艱辛苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我也一定能越過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}讓我們共有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:13.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:45.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:58.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8\fs22}{\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:22.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:27.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:34.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:55.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
